[% if use_celery %]
## Celery

Run worker locally:

```bash
celery -A core worker -l info
```

Redis must be available at `REDIS_URL`.

[% endif %]
[% if use_docker %]
## Docker

Development compose:

```bash
docker compose up -d --build
docker compose exec web python manage.py check
```

See `DOCKER_README.md` for deployment details.

[% endif %]
